ent-BarbedWireBase-name = barbed wire
ent-BarbedWireBase-desc = A type of metal fencing wire constructed with sharp edges or points arranged at intervals along the strands. In short, it hurts to touch it. A lot. Place on barricades to prevent unwants from breaking through painlessly.

